{"words":[{"word":"verbia","count":8},{"word":"glory","count":5},{"word":"arena","count":3},{"word":"ready","count":3},{"word":"hunt","count":3},{"word":"keep","count":2},{"word":"never","count":2},{"word":"falter","count":2},{"word":"aulus","count":2},{"word":"matter","count":2},{"word":"made","count":2},{"word":"gladiator","count":2},{"word":"gladiators","count":2},{"word":"death","count":2},{"word":"i've","count":2},{"word":"opponent","count":2},{"word":"day","count":2},{"word":"dark","count":2},{"word":"reclaim","count":2},{"word":"fight","count":2},{"word":"eat","count":2},{"word":"daughter","count":2},{"word":"long","count":2},{"word":"playername","count":2},{"word":"stance","count":1},{"word":"firm","count":1},{"word":"steady","count":1},{"word":"breath","count":1},{"word":"enemy","count":1},{"word":"coach","count":1},{"word":"father","count":1},{"word":"call","count":1},{"word":"hard","count":1},{"word":"trained","count":1},{"word":"real","count":1},{"word":"makings","count":1},{"word":"septimont's","count":1},{"word":"sharpest","count":1},{"word":"spear","count":1},{"word":"cracked","count":1},{"word":"final","count":1},{"word":"trial","count":1},{"word":"love","count":1},{"word":"ruined","count":1},{"word":"sorry","count":1},{"word":"speak","count":1},{"word":"steel","count":1},{"word":"dance","count":1},{"word":"live","count":1},{"word":"fall","count":1},{"word":"ever","count":1},{"word":"since","count":1},{"word":"match","count":1},{"word":"carried","count":1},{"word":"nothing","count":1},{"word":"regret","count":1},{"word":"maybe","count":1},{"word":"taught","count":1},{"word":"anymore","count":1},{"word":"brightest","count":1},{"word":"student","count":1},{"word":"lost","count":1},{"word":"nerve","count":1},{"word":"stained","count":1},{"word":"shame","count":1},{"word":"lacked","count":1},{"word":"resolve","count":1},{"word":"grant","count":1},{"word":"deserved","count":1},{"word":"hesitate","count":1},{"word":"spare","count":1},{"word":"disgrace","count":1},{"word":"wipe","count":1},{"word":"tears","count":1},{"word":"cloud","count":1},{"word":"vision","count":1},{"word":"dear","count":1},{"word":"gladiator's","count":1},{"word":"given","count":1},{"word":"crowd","count":1},{"word":"lumenstones","count":1},{"word":"unlit","count":1},{"word":"tacet","count":1},{"word":"discords","count":1},{"word":"stalk","count":1},{"word":"hunting","count":1},{"word":"honeycakes","count":1},{"word":"saltimbocca","count":1},{"word":"pack","count":1},{"word":"explain","count":1},{"word":"picky","count":1},{"word":"food","count":1},{"word":"take","count":1},{"word":"share","count":1},{"word":"better","count":1},{"word":"bloodleaves","count":1},{"word":"every","count":1},{"word":"ounce","count":1},{"word":"strength","count":1},{"word":"give","count":1},{"word":"reason","count":1},{"word":"mother's","count":1},{"word":"wisdom","count":1},{"word":"remember","count":1},{"word":"true","count":1},{"word":"cannot","count":1},{"word":"seen","count":1},{"word":"become","count":1},{"word":"enough","count":1},{"word":"tide","count":1},{"word":"sink","count":1},{"word":"teeth","count":1},{"word":"into","count":1},{"word":"must","count":1},{"word":"slay","count":1},{"word":"undying","count":1},{"word":"monster","count":1},{"word":"ah","count":1},{"word":"excuse","count":1},{"word":"lack","count":1},{"word":"propriety","count":1},{"word":"disgraced","count":1},{"word":"champion","count":1},{"word":"great","count":1},{"word":"agon","count":1},{"word":"safe","count":1},{"word":"lies","count":1},{"word":"proud","count":1},{"word":"turn","count":1},{"word":"medulius","count":1},{"word":"dare","count":1},{"word":"desecrate","count":1},{"word":"duel","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"Keep your stance firm and steady your breath, Verbia. Never let your enemy see you falter.","quest_name":"Flames in the Deep","quest_id":151000002},{"text":"…Coach... Father. Aulus. Doesn't matter what you call me. No matter how hard I trained you, you never made it as a real Gladiator.","quest_name":"Flames in the Deep","quest_id":151000002},{"text":"You had the makings of Septimont's sharpest spear… but you cracked in the final trial.","quest_name":"Flames in the Deep","quest_id":151000002},{"text":"It was my love for you that ruined you.","quest_name":"Flames in the Deep","quest_id":151000002},{"text":"Gladiators don't say sorry.","quest_name":"Flames in the Deep","quest_id":151000002},{"text":"We speak with steel. We dance with death. We live and fall for glory.","quest_name":"Flames in the Deep","quest_id":151000002},{"text":"Ever since that match… I've carried nothing but regret. Maybe it was how I taught you that made you falter.","quest_name":"Flames in the Deep","quest_id":151000002},{"text":"Not anymore. My brightest student lost her nerve and stained the arena with shame.","quest_name":"Flames in the Deep","quest_id":151000002},{"text":"You lacked the resolve to grant your opponent the death they deserved.","quest_name":"Flames in the Deep","quest_id":151000002},{"text":"Then why did you hesitate? Why did you spare your opponent? Why did you disgrace the arena of glory?","quest_name":"Flames in the Deep","quest_id":151000002},{"text":"Wipe your tears. They cloud your vision.","quest_name":"Flames in the Deep","quest_id":151000002},{"text":"Verbia, my dear Verbia. A Gladiator's glory is not their own. It's given by the crowd. That day, they were ready. The arena was ready.","quest_name":"Flames in the Deep","quest_id":151000002},{"text":"There are still Lumenstones unlit and Tacet Discords still stalk the dark. We'll keep hunting until the day you're ready to reclaim your glory.","quest_name":"Flames in the Deep","quest_id":151000002},{"text":"Only Honeycakes and no Saltimbocca in your pack? Explain that, Verbia.","quest_name":"Flames in the Deep","quest_id":151000002},{"text":"Don't be picky with your food.","quest_name":"Flames in the Deep","quest_id":151000002},{"text":"Take my share, then. You fight better when you eat well.","quest_name":"Flames in the Deep","quest_id":151000002},{"text":"And eat the Bloodleaves, too. The hunt isn't over. You'll need every ounce of strength.","quest_name":"Flames in the Deep","quest_id":151000002},{"text":"Give me your reason.","quest_name":"Flames in the Deep","quest_id":151000002},{"text":"Tell me, Verbia. Why are we here?","quest_name":"Flames in the Deep","quest_id":151000002},{"text":"You have your mother's wisdom.","quest_name":"Flames in the Deep","quest_id":151000002},{"text":"Remember, Verbia, a true Gladiator can hunt even what cannot be seen.","quest_name":"Flames in the Deep","quest_id":151000002},{"text":"And you, my daughter, will become one.","quest_name":"Flames in the Deep","quest_id":151000002},{"text":"I've been here too long... long enough for the Dark Tide to sink its teeth into me. But you still have a way out.","quest_name":"Flames in the Deep","quest_id":151000002},{"text":"If you want to reclaim your glory, you must slay the undying monster.","quest_name":"Flames in the Deep","quest_id":151000002},{"text":"So come. Hunt me.","quest_name":"Flames in the Deep","quest_id":151000002},{"text":"Ah?! Excuse my lack of propriety, {PlayerName}. I am Aulus, disgraced champion of the Great Agon.","quest_name":"Flames in the Deep","quest_id":151000002},{"text":"Verbia... my daughter... is she safe?","quest_name":"Flames in the Deep","quest_id":151000002},{"text":"There should be no lies between Gladiators, {PlayerName}.","quest_name":"Flames in the Deep","quest_id":151000002},{"text":"Verbia, I'm proud of you. Now, it's my turn to fight.","quest_name":"Flames in the Deep","quest_id":151000002},{"text":"Medulius! How dare you desecrate this duel!","quest_name":"Flames in the Deep","quest_id":151000002}]}